<div id="operate-mgt">
  <div id="operate-intro">
    <h3>Information About Company Column</h3>
    <p>The column is an abstract of "About Company" page. it is only text. The font size is 14px, and the color is orange. The size of the display box is 470x195px.
    <p>In the column, at most, there are 3 paragraphes in it. In one paragraph case, it includes about 770 letters; In two paragraphes case, it has about 700 letters; In three paragraphes case, it has about 630 letters.
    <p>Please review the content as follows.
    </p>
  </div><!-- end #operate-intro -->

  <div id="operate-area">
    <h3>Show About Company Column Content</h3>
    <h5>(The show box size is the same to the column on About Company page.)</h5>
